{"type":"message","id":"81f91795","parentId":"0c26a3d2","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:37:58.436Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要记录这次学习完成的情况到 memory 文件中。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e4b6a1eb205c42e49204ae37","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 2026-04-01 工作记录\n\n## 主要工作\n\n### 1. 验证书籍知识库整理 ✅ 完成\n\n从 `D:\\飞书\\验证书籍` 目录提取并整理所有验证相关书籍。\n\n#### 原始内容提取\n- **PDF 文件**: 19 个\n- **总页数**: 约 6000 页\n- **提取文本**: 7.3 MB（存储在 `raw/` 目录）\n\n#### 结构化知识文档\n生成 10 个知识文档，总计约 114KB：\n\n| 文档 | 大小 | 主要内容 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 01_systemverilog_basics.md | 6KB | SV数据类型、OOP、线程通信 |\n| 02_uvm_framework.md | 7KB | UVM工厂、组件、Phase、Sequence |\n| 03_testbench_architecture.md | 6KB | 分层架构、接口、虚拟接口 |\n| 04_assertions.md | 12KB | 立即断言、并发断言、序列、属性 |\n| 05_coverage.md | 18KB | 代码覆盖、功能覆盖、交叉覆盖 |\n| 06_randomization.md | 14KB | 约束、分布、数组约束 |\n| 07_verification_methodology.md | 20KB | VMM方法论、验证计划 |\n| 08_advanced_topics.md | 13KB | 陷阱规避、性能优化 |\n| 09_practical_cases.md | 13KB | 实战案例、深度学习应用 |\n| ai_verification.md | 5KB | AI时代验证策略 |\n\n#### 书籍来源清单\n1. SystemVerilog for Verification 3rd Edition (500页)\n2. UVM实战（张强）(836页)\n3. UVM1.1应用指南及源码解析 (636页)\n4. Verification Methodology Manual for SystemVerilog (528页)\n5. SystemVerilog功能验证 (221页)\n6. 101个Verilog和SystemVerilog陷阱 (98页)\n7. Verilog Digital System Design (402页)\n8. Fundamentals of Digital Logic with Verilog Design (864页)\n9. 深度学习笔记（1-3册）(1226页)\n10. 其他辅助文档\n\n### 2. 知识库目录结构\n\n```\nknowledge/\n├── verification/           # 验证知识库 ✅\n│   ├── README.md           # 索引\n│   ├── raw/                # 原始提取内容 (7.3MB)\n│   ├── 01_systemverilog_basics.md\n│   ├── 02_uvm_framework.md\n│   ├── 03_testbench_architecture.md\n│   ├── 04_assertions.md\n│   ├── 05_coverage.md\n│   ├── 06_randomization.md\n│   ├── 07_verification_methodology.md\n│   ├── 08_advanced_topics.md\n│   ├── 09_practical_cases.md\n│   └── ai_verification.md\n│\n└── wifi/                   # WiFi 协议知识库\n    ├── README.md\n    ├── phy_basics.md\n    ├── modulation_basics.md\n    ├── dcm.md\n    ├── cordic.md\n    ├── mu_mimo_puncture.md\n    ├── learning_plan.md\n    └── agc_notes.md\n```\n\n---\n\n## 技术要点\n\n### PDF 提取\n- 工具: Python pdfplumber\n- 编码: UTF-8 (忽略错误)\n- 输出: 逐页标记的文本文件\n\n### 知识整理\n- 分类: 按主题划分 9 个核心领域\n- 格式: Markdown + 代码示例 + 表格\n- 特点: 实战导向，包含完整代码示例\n\n---\n\n## 后续使用\n\n### 学习路径推荐\n\n**初学者**:\n1. 01_systemverilog_basics.md → SV基础\n2. 03_testbench_architecture.md → 测试平台\n3. 02_uvm_framework.md → UVM入门\n\n**进阶**:\n1. 04_assertions.md → 断言技术\n2. 05_coverage.md → 覆盖率\n3. 06_randomization.md → 随机化\n\n**专家**:\n1. 07_verification_methodology.md → 方法论\n2. raw/ 目录 → 原始书籍深入阅读\n\n### 快速查找\n- 查看 `README.md` 获取知识点索引\n- 原始内容在 `raw/` 目录，可用 grep 搜索\n\n---\n\n## 待办事项\n\n- [ ] 根据需要补充特定主题的详细内容\n- [ ] 整理 WiFi 协议知识库（已有基础框架）\n- [ ] 建设设计知识库\n","path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_work_robot\\memory\\2026-04-01.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":73146,"output":1097,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74243,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775057833312,"responseId":"b8016033260e970693c31e8992db8910"}}
